Welcome to the prestigious Remraam community by Dubai Properties, located in the heart of Dubailand. This beautifully designed community is the perfect place to call home for families and individuals alike. With easy access to the Dubai Bypass Road and the new airport at Dubai South, Remraam is in a prime location for those seeking convenience and luxury.


At Remraam, you will find two distinct neighborhoods, Al Thamam and Al Ramth, each with 56 low-rise apartment buildings set amidst parkland and served by community facilities. With elegantly designed 1, 2 &amp; 2+ maid bedroom apartments, you will find your perfect home at Remraam.&nbsp;


At Remraam, we offer a range of facilities and amenities to ensure that our residents live a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Take a look at our list of amenities below:





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



Lush green spaces for outdoor activities





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



Family pool and splash parks for everyday refreshment





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



Jogging tracks for exercise and exploration





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



State-of-the-art gymnasium for fitness enthusiasts





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



Swimming pool and beach areas for relaxation





&middot;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 



Various retail outlets for convenience






We understand that purchasing a property is a big decision, which is why we are here to assist you every step of the way. Our team of experienced real estate professionals is here to answer any questions you may have and help guide you through the process.


Don't miss out on the opportunity to call Remraam your home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the luxury and convenience of this beautiful community for yourself.

